Package org.daisy.dotify.api.formatter

Interface VolumeContentBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BlockBuilder, BlockContentBuilder, FormatterCore
    public interface VolumeContentBuilder
extends FormatterCore
    Provides methods needed to build volume anchored content, such as cover pages and TOC.
